quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,17,"∆Āe nanndi ko he ku…ď…ďu…óo jayngol nde ngol yaynii Alla nawi ooyre ma…ď…ďe O acci …ďe e ni…ď…ďe …ďe nji'ataa hay huunde."
  2,18,"Ko fah…óu…ďe muum…óu…ďe wum…ďe …ďe nduttotaako"
  2,19,"Wolla wano to…ďo iwde asamaan wa…óngo ni…ď…ďe e digaali e maje …ďe cukka noppi ma…ď…ďe sabu kartaali (par√Īite) ngam reentaade maayde , Alla noon Ombo fiiltii ge…óe heefer…ďe."
  2,20,"Majal ngal na …óe…ďa diftaade gite ma…ď…ďe kala nde ngal yaynii …ďe njaha heen so ni…ď…ďi…óii …ďe ndaroo, so Alla welano nawa nan…óe e gite ma…ď…ďe sabu Alla ko kattan…óo kala huunde."
  2,21,"Onon yim…ďe ndewee Joom mon tag…óo on tagi adii…ďe on mbela joo kulon Alla."
  2,22,"Oon ba…óan…óo on lesdi ndi mbertu O wa…ói Asamaan o mahoodi tii…óndi O jippini ndiyam iwde e Asamaan O yaltini heen …ďi…ď…ďe le…ó…óe woni nje…óu mon, taa mba…óanee Alla nanndidii…ďe te o…óon nganndi goonga oo."
  2,23,"So tawii o…óon cikkitii e Kur'aana mbo Min njippini dow jeyaa…óo Amen oo, ngaddee simoore nanndunde hembo, noddee wallidii…ďe mon gaa Alla so tawii o…óon ngoong…ói e nodditaandu mon ndu."
  2,24,"So tawii on mba…óaani …óum -te on mba…óataa …óum - kulee jayngol ku…ď…ďirtengol yim…ďe e kaa∆īe, ngol heblanaa ko heefer…ďe …ďee."